Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:10.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,裕美 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 巴酱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 今天天气不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:24.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,开始我们的镰仓观光旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:25.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
